Package aa.test.selenium

Class AA05AuthorizationLevelTest

java.lang.Object
aa.test.utils.AASeleniumManager
aa.test.selenium.AA05AuthorizationLevelTest
@TestMethodOrder(org.junit.jupiter.api.MethodOrderer.OrderAnnotation.class) class AA05AuthorizationLevelTest extends AASeleniumManager
This logs in with the different users to check if they see what they should in the navigation, including both main navigation and sub navigation. It tests all user roles.
